{"tid":300231,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"長文 [垃圾] 旺角榮園麵家","createTime":"2017-06-27T17:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T12:26:13.000Z","uid":8540,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aca882e73ca82ffa64c04423712b8db735969303","tid":300231,"uid":8540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"我同女朋友經過過好多次，見都幾多人食女朋友一直話想試下但之前一次都未食過。<br />\n今日我女朋友自己去開旺角就自己去左食。<br />\n<br />\n佢去到見好多人排緊隊，女朋友擔心影響人地做生意就企係側面空位等，以為等完佢地會安排地方佢坐<br />\n<br />\n之後有個啊叔就態度好差好撚大聲咁話：屌食咩你就講啦！<br />\n我女朋友答佢雲吞河，個啊叔問我女朋友係度食定拎走，女朋友答佢係度食<br />\n<br />\n之後個啊叔就好似食左火藥咁更大聲係度話：係度食就坐啦！人企你又企<br />\n我女朋友答佢第一次係度食唔知，之後女朋友就拎錢想比錢先，因為佢銀包放係背囊度難拎而且佢之後趕住返學所以先想比錢先<br />\n<br />\n啊叔見女朋友拎錢之後又係度鬧：食完先比錢啦！你聽唔聽得明人話啊<br />\n女朋友聽完覺得好嬲，之後問啊叔：你講咩啊 <br />\n之後啊叔就更大聲問返女朋友：講乜撚野唔好啊<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友個時本身已經想走，但之後有幾個男人行出黎，碗麵又整好左，我女朋友見嘈又唔夠佢地多人嘈打又更加冇可能就焗住坐低左食。但d野食實左太難食，雲吞食落唔新鮮湯底又淡到水咁，我女朋友食左兩粒雲吞就起身諗住走。<br />\n<br />\n另一個啊叔知我女朋友都好唔滿意好似驚死我女朋友唔比錢咁，佢個身一郁少少個啊叔已經大叫：收錢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友覺得好委屈喊住咁打比我講返我聽，我聽完真係好嬲，就算係茶記大檔都未試過受咁大氣，食餐飯貼錢買難受。我今日上網睇返間野先知原來間野d態度差都出哂名，我都唔撚明點解間野到今時今日仲可以生存到，不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n相信好多巴打冇食過都有經過過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/010103_30a63aa46fc6d7e69b06fc526f8a40e8.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F010103_30a63aa46fc6d7e69b06fc526f8a40e8.PNG&h=3ae1c917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">間垃圾叫榮園麵家<br />\n狗也不屌，垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"c0ba21af316cb3f065b03a71486e1f60f0b7f826","tid":300231,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f72d5c2b619728ad2bca366bd66f417ac2673ed","tid":300231,"uid":43343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"313f084148e5904e4d517fcefcc80ab6d0514fae","tid":300231,"uid":43343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:15:19.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e97b692c5c0478e291bbf36bbef735b5684df00","tid":300231,"uid":3649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"又貴又細碗又難食，<br />\n我行過見到都唔知點解有人會去食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f87012cf294e2daa7fbb2178ed302823717d34","tid":300231,"uid":1510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:18:06.000Z","msg":"見到個環境 已經唔會入去食 我寧願行返去花園街 求其食一間"},{"pid":"863e7aac68826c709b7e0850065235e1c43a938a","tid":300231,"uid":46894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"嘩屌有次仲諗住去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d765da53f192d70efc651d40eade83d53261a592","tid":300231,"uid":8540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又貴又細碗又難食，<br />\n我行過見到都唔知點解有人會去食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只此一次，提埋未食過ge巴打唔好去食，燒錢"},{"pid":"579a50b74f8432511996484b0146954e586f751d","tid":300231,"uid":117032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"食完個肚有冇覺得唔舒服呀? 有就要搵食環招呼下佢地啦"},{"pid":"7537a84ccc904073e8673df02694fb7579d98012","tid":300231,"uid":8540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食完個肚有冇覺得唔舒服呀? 有就要搵食環招呼下佢地啦</blockquote><br />\n好似有d啊，有冇巴打知大概流程係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1ec19c1cb1d972e932e5abfa696d3e6c53860f","tid":300231,"uid":16039,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"佢啲枱開埋喺條街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> call 埋黑警話疑似阻街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開喺呢啲地方一定有曱甴老鼠啦 叫埋食環睇睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知有冇滅火桶 call 埋消防同佢check check 一間有啲咩事就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecff821402db5f78d3998e1167e1aa6df1fc1bb","tid":300231,"uid":8540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢啲枱開埋喺條街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> call 埋黑警話疑似阻街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開喺呢啲地方一定有曱甴老鼠啦 叫埋食環睇睇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知有冇滅火桶 call 埋消防同佢check check 一間有啲咩事就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係bo 消防真係冇諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f30416275efe730e15efa50e16c92d38d3d46d","tid":300231,"uid":16034,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:31:39.000Z","msg":"你條女on9者 咁都唔走"},{"pid":"8995d98baaa670ae0e9cb9b1ffc7fe070558ea54","tid":300231,"uid":16034,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條女on9者 咁都唔走<br />\n呢個位咁撚多人 撚夠膽打你<br />\n一掂到咪嗌非禮 驚鬼咩 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"fdf14b4341daee39086d04aef20b9fc10de15ca2","tid":300231,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"拿 講畀你聽 隔離地庫間間舖好多小昆蟲 基本上日日要搞 你明唔點解 我就唔係好明啦"},{"pid":"887a120ea187be97984e4a38518816804b053b04","tid":300231,"uid":17556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T21:54:21.000Z","msg":"好撚難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad800dcc4d11f378f165f6fd58ee14027a882a6","tid":300231,"uid":7355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T21:59:13.000Z","msg":"間舖嘅位置已經唔想去食<br />\n利申住旺角附近一次都無食"},{"pid":"11075b5b97dd7edd9fe6020ff537a2accd77bec1","tid":300231,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:04:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9edc91d7f7fea94fe246833c7a0ad613bf078ed","tid":300231,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢試過一次還是不了，一直以為牛腩難食極都唔會好難，呢個真係創新下限"},{"pid":"062f060661352ab294dd436baca78fcba6757086","tid":300231,"uid":8540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你條女on9者 咁都唔走<br />\n呢個位咁撚多人 撚夠膽打你<br />\n一掂到咪嗌非禮 驚鬼咩 </blockquote></blockquote><br />\n啱。男人同人嘈就無優勢。<br />\n正常女仔同人嘈基本上佔盡旁觀者嘅預設同情<br />\n個同情心優勢階梯是咁的: [正常女仔 &gt; mk妹 ＞ 惡女人 &gt; 男人]<br />\n你條女唔好入去坐就得 太淋善了<br />\n<br />\n希望間野仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 佢就係淋得濟所以先比人蝦<br />\n不過聽佢講個啊叔鬧佢個時都冇人理冇人出聲，個個有事個時都只會係食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12e3e6985a24baad6cd168960e94d9519b5a366","tid":300231,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"呢間都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21084408cd5ffb9b1e4e27277cd0b84affa4f251","tid":300231,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ef6a49b39281eee8f2eb9ff35252d846ec4af0","tid":300231,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"由細食到大都冇事喎..."},{"pid":"22a97df681a226d4d794cb4f2c18c9cf670b10d0","tid":300231,"uid":9651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"而家難食左"},{"pid":"ca8d34aec8ac0217da8c03521e7f41c2b7481fdf","tid":300231,"uid":43308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}